here if the connection is not working while checking the api in postman these are the steps to follow 
1. first click on the header tab and check for the content type is in json/application if not add 
2. in the lost u see a json icon click on it manually insert the data if for register you insert data like 
{
  "name": "Sanjay",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "is_admin": true
}
 into it 
3. then click on the send then you will receive the ouput in the body 